798
00:35:25,600 --> 00:35:30,120
Okay, so you're going to want to go to those buns dough?

799
00:35:30,120 --> 00:35:31,960
Perfect, saw it walking in, yes.

800
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:34,039
Delicious, delicious.

801
00:35:34,039 --> 00:35:35,679
Coffee, pastries, wonderful.

802
00:35:35,679 --> 00:35:37,400
Pulls out a little flip notebook

803
